[div class=p 
	"As best I understand it, some aspects of the game's timing were changed for the PAL release (such as Little Mac's movement speed) while other aspects were not altered (including opponent speeds).  These types of differences allow for variations in strategies against the opponents compared to those strats used in an NTSC run.
	$LF
